data.description: Introducing a stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, home in south Victorville. This recently remodeled home boasts a modern kitchen and bathrooms, providing both style and functionality. For horse enthusiasts, this property is a dream come true with ample space to accommodate up to three horses. You will find an extra room in the garage, perfect for a home office. Entertain in style in the barbecue area with a gas connection, fire pit, and a large bar outside while enjoying the breathtaking desert backdrop. An additional bonus room outdoors, offers endless possibilities - from a cozy outdoor lounge to a play area for the kids, to extra storage. A large area dedicated as a workshop makes this property perfect for large equipment operators or anyone needing space for big trucks. A small basketball court, RV Parking and let's not forget all the little details: tinted windows all around the house to keep it cool on those hot days, misters in the patio, and a bluetooth speaker in the bathroom! Don't miss all the opportunities this desert gem has to offer with beauty, comfort, and close to the freeway/highway for easy commuting!
